The vendored files live under src/pcaone. The reproducible recipe and pinned
source archive are under tools/vendor-pcaone. Common.hpp omits PCAone's unused
zstd include. Logger.hpp initializes the screen flag and routes optional output
through R's console. Utils.hpp and Utils.cpp retain only the helper closure used
by the randomized-SVD path. These adaptations remain under GPL-3; no upstream
code is relicensed.
